Name: Xorsat
AboutMe:
Started in 2010, [XORSAT][1] has evolved as a leading IT Application Development center, coupled with a cost-effective and easily accessible Outsourcing Solution.

Xorsat has successfully built numerous mobile and web applications which have added value to our customers and helped their businesses grow faster than ever. Our highly skilled software development professionals are committed to provide best solutions using cutting edge technologies. While respecting your business needs, our technical team provides smart and alternate suggestions to help you choose better option.

Xorsat.com is a leading, offshore web development service provider catering result-oriented and cost-competitive solutions to SMEs. With our solid domain experience, technical expertise and profound knowledge, we continue to deliver latest industry trends and quality-driven successful implementation of end-to-end web solutions.

The IT Application Development Processes and Remote Resource Management Systems that we have devised, are the two lenses of a binocular through which you can examine and keep-in-touch with our resources. We understand the quality and dedication your business demands, based on that we appoint a committed and dedicated team to our customers.
